---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Startup Advisory" description="Nikhil Kulkarni's startup advisory work: helping early-stage founders with product strategy, go-to-market, and growth.">

  <div class="page-header">
    <p class="page-label">AI &amp; Product</p>
    <h1>Startup Advisory</h1>
    <p class="intro">Working with early-stage founders on product strategy, go-to-market, and what it actually takes to build something people want.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <section class="section">
      <h2>What I bring</h2>
      <p>Nearly two decades of product and technology experience, from early-stage Indian startups to Flipkart and 7.5 years at Atlassian, including founding PM lead for Rovo, Atlassian's AI product. I've built products across e-commerce, B2B SaaS, education, social networking, and AI, at every stage from idea to global scale.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Where's the best fit?</h2>
      <p>I work best with founders who are figuring out product-market fit, building their first team, or thinking through how to position AI in their product.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>How I work</h2>
      <p>I ask sharp questions, push back where needed, and bring both a practitioner's perspective and an investor's eye.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Where I can help</h2>

      <div class="help-group">
        <h3 class="help-group-title">Strategic growth &amp; go-to-market</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid">
          <div class="area-card">
            <h4>Customer development &amp; GTM</h4>
            <p>Helping founders define their Ideal Customer Profile, refine outreach narratives and channels, and land their first non-friends-and-family customers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <h4>Storytelling &amp; narrative</h4>
            <p>Refining value propositions and communicating them effectively to investors, employees, and customers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="help-group">
        <h3 class="help-group-title">Product &amp; operational expertise</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid">
          <div class="area-card">
            <h4>Product craft</h4>
            <p>Helping teams build, scale, and mature their product functions, from early-stage chaos to structured, high-performing product practice.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <h4>AI advisory</h4>
            <p>A critical and intentional lens on AI adoption, identifying where it makes sense to build or implement AI and how to demonstrate clear value rather than just capability.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="help-group">
        <h3 class="help-group-title">Facilitation &amp; ecosystem</h3>
        <div class="areas-grid">
          <div class="area-card">
            <h4>Networking &amp; introductions</h4>
            <p>Facilitating high-value connections between founders, investors, and mentors across ecosystems.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="area-card">
            <h4>Mentorship &amp; advisory</h4>
            <p>Ongoing support as a thought partner and sounding board, showing up consistently, not just at the crisis moments.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>I'm selective about advisory engagements: I'd rather go deep with a small number of founders than spread thin. If you're working on something interesting and think there's a fit, I'd like to hear about it.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-btn">Get in touch</a>
    </section>

  </div>

</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 3rem 0 0.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .page-label {
    font-family: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c2613f;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .content { max-width: 760px; }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #474747;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .help-group {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .help-group:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .help-group-title {
    font-family: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .areas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .area-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
    border-top: 3px solid #c2613f;
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h4 {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .area-card p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: #555;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: #c2613f;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.4rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-btn:hover { background: #a84e30; }
</style>
